{"id":91824,"title":"Service user involvement in nurse education.","abstract":"Service user involvement is now recognised as an integral component of nurse education. This article describes the involvement of one service user, who experienced a traumatic limb amputation, in an educational session for second-year nursing students at De Montfort University. The aim of the initiative was to use the patient's experience to improve care delivery. ","date":"2014-01-29","categories":"Wounds and Injuries","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24471636","annotations":[{"name":"De Montfort University","weight":0.847992,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/De_Montfort_University"},{"name":"Nurse education","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nurse_education"},{"name":"Amputation","weight":0.0279372,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amputation"},{"name":"Education","weight":0.0227187,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Education"},{"name":"Integral","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Integral"},{"name":"Session musician","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Session_musician"},{"name":"Limb (anatomy)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Limb_(anatomy)"},{"name":"User (computing)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User_(computing)"},{"name":"Nurse","weight":0.0163827,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nurse"},{"name":"County of Montfort (Vorarlberg)","weight":0.0157947,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/County_of_Montfort_(Vorarlberg)"},{"name":"Initiative","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Initiative"},{"name":"Trauma (medicine)","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trauma_(medicine)"},{"name":"Nursing","weight":0.014492,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipe